item.title: Meetup - Tuesday 11th October 2016 at The ODI Node in Leeds
item.description: Do you like to party ? You do ? then join us on Tuesday 11th October at the ODI Node in Leeds to celebrate not only Ada Lovelace day but the 3rd birthday of Leeds Devops! Join us for: 6:45 - 7:15 : Doors open, have a chat, make some new devops friends 7:15 - 7:30 : Group updates/news/announcements 7:30 - 8:00 : Design Patterns for Git - Lorna Mitchell
